MarketPulse AI: Predictive Analytics for Financial Market Insights

MarketPulse AI uses machine learning and deep learning to predict market movements by analyzing financial data, sentiment from social media, and macroeconomic indicators.

Features:
- Real-time market data ingestion
- Sentiment analysis using HuggingFace Transformers
- Forecasting models with LSTM and XGBoost
- Interactive Streamlit dashboard to visualize predictions

How to Run the Project:
1. Clone the repository:
   git clone https://github.com/MohdRaza-Firoj-Deshpande/MarketPulse-Al.git
2. Change directory into the project folder:
   cd MarketPulse-Al
3. Install Python dependencies:
   pip install -r requirements.txt
4. Run the Streamlit dashboard app:
   streamlit run app/dashboard.py

Project Structure:
MarketPulse-Al/
├── data/               # Raw and processed financial and sentiment data files
├── notebooks/          # Jupyter notebooks for exploratory data analysis and experiments
├── src/                # Source code for model training and utilities
├── app/                # Streamlit dashboard application files
├── requirements.txt    # Python library dependencies
└── README.md           # Project overview and instructions

Future Work:
